   buscas %>%
        group_by(data = as.Date(session_start_date), group) %>% 
        summarise(clickthrough = sum(num_clicks > 0)/n()) %>%
        ggplot(aes(x = as.Date(data), y = clickthrough, fill = group)) + 
        geom_col(position = "dodge") +
        scale_x_date('Data', date_labels = "%b %d") +
        labs(y= "propor√ß√£o de clickthrough", title="Figura 1 -")
